headline: High Growth Tech Stocks To Watch In December 2024
summary: Over the last 7 days, the United States market has dropped 4.0%, but it remains up by 24% over the past year with earnings expected to grow by 15% annually in the coming years. In this dynamic environment, identifying high growth tech stocks involves looking at companies with strong innovation potential and robust financial health that can capitalize on anticipated earnings growth.
